Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.24,0:00:27.13,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs204\fnGallow Tree\bord2\4aFF\\pos(1094,814)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.54,0:00:27.63,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.25,0:00:30.92,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With its armies \Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:35.18,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadow\N threatens us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.47,0:00:38.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,But I'll fight to maintain\N the peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:42.56,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.77,0:00:46.02,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.44,0:00:48.90,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.11,0:00:52.53,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.70,0:00:57.24,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:01:00.74,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.04,0:01:03.33,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.54,0:01:07.17,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:11.67,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.67,0:01:15.13,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.74,0:01:35.99,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an9}Daidouji Geophysics\N Research Institute
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.99,0:01:44.00,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx90\fs183\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\\b1\pos(1649.787,169.928)}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.99,0:01:44.00,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs230\bord0\4aFF\fnCienfuegos\b1\\pos(1684.572,323.979)}Versus
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.99,0:01:44.00,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs183\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\\b1\pos(1667.142,478.858)}Shocker
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.16,0:01:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ano, the experiment \Nwas a huge success!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.88,0:01:50.59,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,I'm really happy for you, professor. {F: i looked into it more and Daidouji's title seem to be 博士 (hakase) which usually is translated as "doctor". "professor" in japanese is usually 教授 (kyoujuu). however, i am not well versed enough in academia terms to know which would apply better for him}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.55,0:01:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.55,0:01:56.38,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{If the artificial gravity device GX is able to be\N enlarged it could even shifts the earth's axis.}If the artificial gravity device GX was larger,\Nit could be strong enough to shift the Earth's axis!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.68,0:02:00.05,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{But it'd be a disaster if \Nused for evil purposes, right?}It would be a disaster if it fell into the wrong hands, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.{そうだよ　世界を簡単に\N征服されてしまう}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.06,0:02:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{It'd be simple to force the world \Nto unconditionally surrender.}Even world conquest would be an easy task.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.54,0:02:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- All right.\N- Let's go process the experiment data.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the data ready to be \Ninputted into the computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:29.70,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{Ano, we have to hurry and\N pick up the experiments data!}Ano, hurry up and help me gather the data!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.68,0:02:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.01,0:02:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A power outage?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:39.80,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{The lightning is probably the culprit.}Maybe because of the lightning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.85,0:02:43.56,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,Professor Daidouji!{大道寺博士}{a note but do you wanna spell it Daidouji or Daidoji, since we seem to use Hongo and not Hongou}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:46.84,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{I congratulate you for completing your research.}{研究の完成 お祝いする}I want to congratulate you on \Ncompleting your research.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.36,0:02:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's There!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.78,0:02:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We are Shocker, and we have waited\N patiently for your research to bare fruit.{我々 ショッカーは お前の研究を\Nじっと待っていたのだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.70,0:02:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Doctor Shinigami, The Commander \Nof Shocker's Japan branch.{ショッカー日本支部の指揮官 死神博士}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.75,0:03:12.98,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{Shocker is grateful to you for handing your research over.}{お前の研究はショッカーが ありがたく\Nちょうだいすることになる}We will now gratefully take \Nthe fruits of your research!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't hand it over! \NGet out of here, Ano!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right.\N- Hurry and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.35,0:03:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Ano?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.08,0:03:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ano!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor! \NHelp me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.07,0:03:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You shall not escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:45.51,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{By altering the Earth's axis, Shocker will be able to rule the world.}{地球の地軸を\N変えることができれば ショッカーは世界を支配できる}If Shocker holds the power has the power to shift \Nthe Earth's axis, we will be able to subjugate the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ano!\N Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:50.21,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{Return Ano!}What'd you do with Ano?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Release him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:32.46,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,Begin constructing the artificial \Ngravity device using the data at once.{そのデータから 直ちに 人工重力装置の組み立てに\N取り掛かれ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:40.05,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,We will alter the Earth's axis, and sink the\N Japanese archipelago into the bottom of the sea!{地球の地軸を変えて この日本列島を\N海の底に沈めてやる}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:48.01,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{May I say something, Doctor Shinigami?}Excuse me, Doctor Shinigami?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.87,0:04:52.18,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{The most important part, the GX equation, is missing from this data.}{このデータには最も重要な\NＧＸの方程式が 載っておりませんが…}This data is missing it's most\N vital part, the GX equation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare he!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:05:00.44,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{So that scoundrel Daidouji hid this crucial portion?}{大道寺め 肝心な部分を\N隠しておったのか}That damn Daidouji must have hidden\N the most crucial piece of the puzzle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{Shocker does not give up just like that!}{このまま引き下がる\Nショッカーではない}However, we will not give up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:15.08,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{\i1}{渡してはならない}I will never hand it over...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I put my blood, sweat and tears into that research.\NNo way I'd give it up to benefit a world domination conspiracy!}{俺が命を懸けた研究を\N世界征服の陰謀のためになど 使われてたまるものか\i1}I will not let my life's work be used for world domination!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ano?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ano!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Ano!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ano! You've gotta get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.49,0:05:51.62,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{Are you all right?}So you're alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:53.58,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{That must have been horrible. I'm sorry.}{ひどい目に遭ったな　すまん}I've put you through a lot, so please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to get you to a hospital.{すぐ 病院に連れていくぞ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have been hard to escape.{よく逃げてこられたな}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad that you're okay.{本当に助かってよかった}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.43,0:06:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...{いや }
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,While they were shocked learning that the GX \Nequation wasn't included in the data they stole{奴らは 奪ったデータに\NＧＸの方程式がないと知って}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I took a chance and escaped.{私は その隙に…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.74,0:06:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Pr-professor...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Just where where in the world \Ndid you hide the GX equation?{一体 ＧＸの方程式は\Nどこに隠しておかれたんです？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you, I entrusted it to my daughter, \NTamami, in case anything happened.{万一の場合を考えて 実は娘の珠美に預けておいたんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's with Tamami...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ano?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Fly Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:54.68,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{Good job blurting out the truth!}I'll thank you for blabbering the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,, With it's location confirmed,\N we have no more use for you, Daidouji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot escape us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! I only ask that you \Nspare my daughter, Tamami!{頼む　娘だけは… 珠美だけは助けてくれ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.47,0:07:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let her go in peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.68,0:07:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg of you! please spare my daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll only consider it if you hand over\N the GX equation willingly. {おとなしくＧＸの秘密を渡せばな}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:37.68,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,Stop right there, Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:41.65,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{Do not say it!}Don't tell them anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've shown yourself, FBI brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker! We won't let you take Professor Daidouji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato, how did you know where we were?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The FBI headquarters deciphered \Nyour encrypted transmissions!{ＦＢＩ本部が貴様たちの\N極秘暗号通信を解読したんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:10.33,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{Targeting Professor Daidouji's research in order to flood the Earth, aren't you?}{大道寺博士の研究を狙い\N地球を水浸しにする作戦をな}You're aiming for Professor Daidouji's research\Nin order to flood the world, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.33,0:08:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, take care of the Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Come at me, Ichimonji Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're here as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabotegron and Mogurang!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Shocker cyborgs!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you do that to our comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.72,0:09:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me on if you dare, Fly Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.86,0:10:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We arrived just in time, didn't we?{危なく 間に合わないところでしたね}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right now, Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.01,0:10:15.72,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,It's not. We might be too late.{いや 遅い　遅いかもしれません}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:18.09,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,For what reason?\N Why are we too late?{何がです？どうして遅いんですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I already told them that the secret of my \Nresearch is being held by my daughter.{研究の秘密が娘のところにあると\Nしゃべってしまったんです}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.02,0:10:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,With your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:30.77,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fscx120\fs153\bord5.1\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&H221E22&\3c&H485B6F&\b1\pos(1288.002,133.998)}Daidouji
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamami, here's something on behalf of everyone.{珠美くん　みんなを代表して\N僕からひと言}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.95,0:10:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thank you!\N- Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't you feel lonely without your father here?{でもさ お父さん 来ないと\N寂しいだろ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamami's father is a famous scientist, \Nso it can't be helped.{珠美ちゃんのお父さんは\N有名な科学者なんですもの 仕方ないわね}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. I've gotten used to it.{私 慣れてるから平気よ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.35,0:10:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{Even though Papa didn't come, I still have lots of friends who did.}{パパがいなくても\Nたくさんのお友達が来てくれたし}Even if my Papa's not around,\Nall my friends are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, he didn't forget, \Nbecause he sent me a present.{それに パパはちゃんと忘れないで\Nプレゼントを送ってくれたのよ ね}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.27,0:11:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Your doll is cool and all, \Nbut the cake is even better!{でも 人形もすごいけど\Nケーキもすげえな}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! That's right!{あら ごめんなさい\Nじゃ 切らなくちゃ} \NI still haven't cut it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to blow the candles out first?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.02,0:11:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, close the curtains. \NIt'll give off a nice glow!{おい カーテン 閉めてくれよ 暗くしてムードを出そうや}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Blow it all out with one breath!{ひと息で消すんだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.53,0:11:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready? Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The cake's on fire!\N We need to get out of here!{みんな　ドアから逃げろ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,W- What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.37,0:11:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- But what's wrong with it?\N- The door's stuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The only option left is to go\N through the windows, let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Shocker cyborgs are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.88,0:11:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.64,0:11:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Arigabari and Dokugander, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that!\N It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- You brat!\N- Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.07,0:12:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- Crap.\N- Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Speed it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.01,0:12:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, sleeping on the job, are you?{おい 何をグズグズしてるんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.43,0:12:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He's unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knocked him out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Hongo Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.84,0:12:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker cyborgs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:38.67,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{Leave that girl behind and retreat obediently!}{その娘を置いて\Nおとなしく退散したまえ}Put down that girl and leave immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:43.36,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,Silence! {We'll take your life if you get in our way!}If you dare to interfere\N then your life is forfeit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:45.20,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{I'll show you what happens when you defy me!}{私の言葉が聞こえないと見える}It seems like you couldn't hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.54,0:12:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(960,769.714)}Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.82,0:13:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay behind me, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.80,0:14:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Save me, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.08,0:14:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're an all new cyborg?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.91,0:14:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Zanjioh! I'm a man-eating\N salamander from the Japanese Alps!{日本アルプスにすむ\N人食いサンショウウオ その名はザンジオーだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:15:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl is ours, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Good timing, Ichimonji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We've captured the girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad! \NThey've taken the Professor's daughter.{しまった　博士のお嬢さんを…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a fearsome Shocker cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:56.93,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,Please cheer up a little, Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:16:00.27,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{Even our Chief has such a grave face.}{会長まで\Nそんな難しい顔しちゃって}You should too, Pops. \NYou look very distraught.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:03.31,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{They'll get Tamami back for sure!}{隼人さんたち きっと\N珠美ちゃんを連れて戻るわよ}I'm sure Hayato will come back with Tamami soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:08.74,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{A parent's concern for his child is something immeasurable.}{子供の身を案ずる\N親の気持ちっていうのは それは大変なもんだ}A parent can't help but be concerned\N about their child's well being.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:16.03,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{But you all probably do not understand that yet.}{もっとも 今のお前たちには 分かれというのが\N無理かもしれんがな}Though, I don't expect you girls to\N understand what that feels like yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.45,0:16:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,W- What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He suffered a light concussion, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw man... \NWhy those Shocker creeps!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the Professor's daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We were too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.32,0:16:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.09,0:16:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She was taken by Shocker.{襲ったのはショッカーです\Nやっぱり}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as we feared...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.53,0:16:58.58,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,Yes, this is Tachibana Racing Club—{はい 立花レーシングクラブで…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Doctor Shinigami?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:06.52,Italics,,0,0,0,,{You better tell this to Professor Daidouji.}Deliver this message to Professor Daidouji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If he values his daughter's life, \Nthen he will hand over the GX equation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The exchange will be held at Hell Valley.{personally i prefer keeping JP location names still in JP, so here it would be Jigoku Valley}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.93,0:17:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow at noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker!{ショッカー　大道寺博士を\Nお連れしたぞ} \NI've brought Professor Daidouji as requested!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.14,0:17:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to return Tamami?{珠美ちゃんを渡してもらおうか}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.44,0:18:08.73,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{Thanks for coming}So you've finally come, Ichimonji Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.32,0:18:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The exchange will be done \Nin the middle of the valley.{人質交換は 谷の中央で行う}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,On the count of three, we will begin!{今から３つ数えたら歩き出せ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If you try to do anything, \Nwe'll kill the girl!{変なまねをすれば娘は殺す}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.69,0:18:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamami wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think that Shocker would \Nlet you just walk away?{貴様をこのまま無事に帰す\Nショッカーか}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You fell right into our trap!{貴様は わなの真っただ中だ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mukadelas!{ムカデラス\Nカメストーン}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamestone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.57,0:19:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Armadillong!{アルマジロング\Nナメクジラ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Namekujira!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Zanbronzo!{ザンブロンゾ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Egyptas!{エジプタス}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghoster!{ゴースター\Nユニコルノス}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Unicornos!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Crab Bubbler!{カニバブラー\N狼男}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolf Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Todogiller!{トドギラー\Nドクダリアン}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Dokudalian!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Antlithunder!{地獄サンダー\N蜘蛛男}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:53.71,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,Spider Man!{isnt it officially Man Spider}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Gamagiller!{ガマギラー\Nドクガンダー}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Dokugander!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamogerus!{ヤモゲラス\Nエイキング}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:19:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Eiking!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Snowman!{スノーマン\Nさそり男}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Scorpion Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Isoginchack!{イソギンチャック\N蝙蝠男}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.43,0:20:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Bat Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.93,0:20:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Torikabuto!{トリカブト\Nゲバコンドル}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Gebacondor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Chameleon!{カメレオン\Nアリキメデス}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Arichimedes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Musasabeedle!{ムササビドール\Nサラセニアン}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sarracenian!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.82,0:20:19.19,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{It does not matter if you are immortal.}{貴様が いかに不死身であろうとも}Even if you consider yourself invincible
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you stand no chance against our great army!{大軍団を相手に 万に一つの勝ち目はあるまい}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you gone mad, Ichimonji Hayato?{くるったか 一文字隼人}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.40,0:20:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that your over confidence has made you blind.{己の策に溺れて 目がよく見えんらしいな}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a good look at the Professor Daidouji you have!{お前が捕らえた大道寺博士を\Nよく見ろ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.86,0:20:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:59.25,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{You will accompany us until the three of us reach a safe place.}{私たち３人を安全な場所まで\N案内していただこう}You'll be coming with us until we reach safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.25,0:21:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You planned this, didn't you, Hongo Takeshi?{はかったな 本郷猛}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.49,0:21:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell that group of ravenous monsters\N to get out of our sight!{あの物騒な連中に\N消えろと言うんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.11,0:21:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- Now...\N- Hongo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let's take a walk, shall we?\N- Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.31,0:21:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hold on tight!{しっかりつかまってるんだ}\N- Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.85,0:21:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.69,0:21:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.77,0:21:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,None of you will leave here alive!{うぬら　生きて帰さん}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.41,0:21:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.71,0:21:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamami!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.71,0:21:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.68,0:22:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be afraid, Tamami!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.14,0:22:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your eyes closed no matter what, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.23,0:22:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. \NI'll do like you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.82,0:22:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo! It's time to Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.90,0:22:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.53,0:22:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,799)}Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.67,0:22:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,799)}Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.62,0:23:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Hammer Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.73,0:23:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Shocker cyborgs!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.20,0:23:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato, leave them to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.25,0:24:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Will he be all right alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.67,0:24:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.40,0:24:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.84,0:24:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What good timing! \NTake care of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.92,0:24:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.26,0:24:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,, - All right!\N- Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.11,0:24:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.18,0:24:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.18,0:24:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.27,0:24:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you prepared yourselves, Riders?{ライダー　覚悟はいいな}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.67,0:25:18.19,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kicking off the ground\Nwith a Rider Jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.19,0:25:25.07,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,a great turbine that\Nwhirls through the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.37,0:25:29.07,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Calling up lightning\Nwith a Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.07,0:25:32.74,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies\Nwith a Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.74,0:25:36.45,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.45,0:25:40.04,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.91,0:26:06.40,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tearing through the\Nair with a Rider Plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.40,0:26:12.98,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,a great flight that\Nskates over the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.93,0:26:17.77,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Calling up tornadoes\Nwith a Rider Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.79,0:26:21.51,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies\Nwith a Rider Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.51,0:26:25.19,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.19,0:26:28.91,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.93,0:24:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.14,0:25:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.14,0:25:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let's do this.\N- Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.62,0:25:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.55,0:26:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{We've gotten rid of all of them.}{これで全部 片づいた}That was the last of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.96,0:26:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange. Zanjioh wasn't with them.{おかしい ザンジオーがいなかった}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.89,0:26:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.16,0:26:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamami!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.74,0:26:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.79,0:26:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.96,0:26:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But I stayed strong for you Papa.{でも\Nパパのためだと思って 我慢してたの}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.25,0:26:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I never wanted to put you \Nin danger because of my research.{あんな研究をしたばっかりに\N危ない目に遭わせて}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.00,0:26:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor, about your research...{博士　その研究なんですが}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.71,0:26:59.09,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{In what way did you leave the secret with your daughter?}{一体 その秘密を お嬢さんにどんな方法で\N渡してあったんですか}How exactly did you leave the\N secret information your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.18,0:27:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's in the doll I gave Tamami as her birthday present.{実は 珠美の誕生日の\Nプレゼントとして送った 人形の中に}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.48,0:27:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In a doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.14,0:27:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where is that doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.79,0:27:12.02,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,It's still at home.{うちに置いたままよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.26,0:27:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.96,0:27:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.76,0:27:40.07,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{I cannot let you have the doll!}{この人形を\N貴様に渡すわけにはいかん}I won't let you have this doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.52,0:27:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.44,0:27:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.95,0:28:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.99,0:28:06.68,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,When we were attacked, we didn't see you anywhere.{私たちを襲った中に\Nお前の姿はなかった}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.75,0:28:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,we assumed that meant you were secretly\N following us to get the secrets of the GX equation!{ということは\Nひそかに俺たちをつけて ＧＸの秘密を\N狙っていたことになる}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.17,0:28:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.53,0:28:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.00,0:28:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.00,0:28:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo! Go after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.43,0:29:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't escape, Zanjioh!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.76,0:29:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.07,0:29:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that, Riders?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.75,0:29:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Riders!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.97,0:29:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there, Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.97,0:29:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.89,0:30:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Double Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.23,0:31:21.31,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.86,0:31:24.61,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With its armies made of demons
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.40,0:31:28.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten our friends
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.99,0:31:32.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,But I'll fight to maintain the peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.62,0:31:36.08,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.29,0:31:39.54,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my scarf of red...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.96,0:31:42.42,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.63,0:31:46.05,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.21,0:31:50.76,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.76,0:31:54.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.56,0:31:56.85,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.06,0:32:00.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.65,0:32:05.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.19,0:32:08.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
